CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 16, 1954, pg. 6, reads: "Carver Luncheon - The tenth annual observance of George Washington Carver Week was highlighted with a luncheon at the Sheraton Hotel on Wednesday...In the center photo, Mrs. Robert L. Vann's surprise registers as she is presented with the Amvets National Certificate of Merit by the national commander of the veterans' group, Henry K. Mahady..."
TitMainTitle: Henry J. Mahady, presenting Jessie Vann with Amvets National Certificate of Merit, and Alma Illery, gathered at table in Penn Sheraton hotel for George Washington Carver luncheon
